  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile, pending signature)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is filed under the Minimal profile; a content hash is recorded but the digital signature has not yet been applied — the signature workflow is pending organizational PKI provisioning. Full 13-factor assessment is included. Decision: Accepted (conditional on signature completion).",
